    <item>
      <title>用本地 AI 自动生成文章简介和标签：LM Studio 实践</title>
      <link>https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/p/%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0-ai-%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B%E5%92%8C%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BElm-studio-%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 21:25:37 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/p/%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0-ai-%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B%E5%92%8C%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BElm-studio-%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;在编写文章的过程中，我常常会遇到怎么写简介可以让人一眼看出你想讲什么，以及给文章打上什么标签和分类，这些繁琐的工作常常消耗了我大量的精力（特别是文章多的时候），那么为了专注于文章内容本身，我们可以借助&lt;strong&gt;ai&lt;/strong&gt;来帮助我们在发布之前就进行补全，在开始先介绍一下我的电脑配置，有助于如何选择合适的&lt;strong&gt;大模型&lt;/strong&gt;，如下图&lt;span class=&#34;stack-lazy-picture&#34; data-lazy-state=&#34;preview&#34;&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/avif&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9f8203b40418/f4728d12040f/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/webp&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9f8203b40418/f4728d12040f/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9f8203b40418/f4728d12040f/responsive_content-placeholder-320.jpg&#34;&#xA;    width=&#34;1440&#34;&#xA;    height=&#34;843&#34;&#xA;    data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9f8203b40418/f4728d12040f/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9f8203b40418/f4728d12040f/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg&#34;&#xA;    data-native-src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9f8203b40418/f4728d12040f/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg&#34;&#xA;    data-native-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9f8203b40418/f4728d12040f/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg 1440w&#34;&#xA;    sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;low&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;alt text&#34;&#xA;    data-image-state=&#34;loading&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;gallery-image stack-lazy-image&#34;&#xA;    data-lazy-image=&#34;true&#34; data-lazy-state=&#34;preview&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-enabled=&#34;true&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-strategy=&#34;eager&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-avif=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9f8203b40418/f4728d12040f/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-webp=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9f8203b40418/f4728d12040f/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-fallback=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9f8203b40418/f4728d12040f/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;410px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;170&#34;&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;/span&gt;主要看显卡显存和内存大小，8G显存这一级别下，最优解应该是qwen3.6 35b a3b模型，专家架构可以显著提高输出速度，减少性能需求，选择了大模型后，接下来就是选择管理大模型的工具了，最主流的应该是&lt;strong&gt;LM studio&lt;/strong&gt;和&lt;strong&gt;ollama&lt;/strong&gt;，在这里我推荐LM studio，因为它有图形化界面，配置方便，下面是针对本机的参数调整界面&lt;span class=&#34;stack-lazy-picture&#34; data-lazy-state=&#34;preview&#34;&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/avif&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/81554606fd6f/9ec53595a79b/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/webp&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/81554606fd6f/9ec53595a79b/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/81554606fd6f/9ec53595a79b/responsive_content-placeholder-320.jpg&#34;&#xA;    width=&#34;1440&#34;&#xA;    height=&#34;859&#34;&#xA;    data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/81554606fd6f/9ec53595a79b/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/81554606fd6f/9ec53595a79b/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg&#34;&#xA;    data-native-src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/81554606fd6f/9ec53595a79b/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg&#34;&#xA;    data-native-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/81554606fd6f/9ec53595a79b/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg 1440w&#34;&#xA;    sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;low&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;alt text&#34;&#xA;    data-image-state=&#34;loading&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;gallery-image stack-lazy-image&#34;&#xA;    data-lazy-image=&#34;true&#34; data-lazy-state=&#34;preview&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-enabled=&#34;true&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-strategy=&#34;eager&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-avif=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/81554606fd6f/9ec53595a79b/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-webp=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/81554606fd6f/9ec53595a79b/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-fallback=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/81554606fd6f/9ec53595a79b/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;402px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;167&#34;&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;/span&gt;实测处理单篇博文可以达到30token/s，接下来遇到的难题是怎么连到原有的部署流程，这涉及到程序之间端口的通讯，恰好LM studio有方便的本地端口1234，具体实现可以用ai写&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>寒假总结：博客备案、CDN 加速和服务器项目落地</title>
      <link>https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/p/%E5%AF%92%E5%81%87%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88cdn-%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E5%92%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%90%BD%E5%9C%B0/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 05:04:26 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/p/%E5%AF%92%E5%81%87%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88cdn-%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E5%92%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%90%BD%E5%9C%B0/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;del&gt;啊啊啊，我不要上学啊&lt;/del&gt;，看看我在高一后的寒假里都做了点什么吧。&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;重点-1满-16-周岁--备案完成&#34;&gt;重点 1：满 16 周岁 + 备案完成&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;首先重头戏的那肯定就是&lt;strong&gt;满 16 周岁&lt;/strong&gt;，所以在寒假期间我给我的域名整了&lt;strong&gt;icp 备案&lt;/strong&gt;以及&lt;strong&gt;公安备案&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;stack-lazy-picture&#34; data-lazy-state=&#34;preview&#34;&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/avif&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/8de232410a52/116b0b7df3a0/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/webp&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/8de232410a52/116b0b7df3a0/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/8de232410a52/116b0b7df3a0/responsive_content-placeholder-320.jpg&#34;&#xA;    width=&#34;1440&#34;&#xA;    height=&#34;782&#34;&#xA;    data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/8de232410a52/116b0b7df3a0/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/8de232410a52/116b0b7df3a0/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg&#34;&#xA;    data-native-src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/8de232410a52/116b0b7df3a0/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg&#34;&#xA;    data-native-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/8de232410a52/116b0b7df3a0/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg 1440w&#34;&#xA;    sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;low&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;&#34;&#xA;    data-image-state=&#34;loading&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;gallery-image stack-lazy-image&#34;&#xA;    data-lazy-image=&#34;true&#34; data-lazy-state=&#34;preview&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-enabled=&#34;true&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-strategy=&#34;eager&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-avif=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/8de232410a52/116b0b7df3a0/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-webp=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/8de232410a52/116b0b7df3a0/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-fallback=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/8de232410a52/116b0b7df3a0/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;441px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;184&#34;&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
